- F004（同层排序）: 通过。`_layered_topo_sort()` 已引入并在 `plan_learning_path()` 用 `gap_score` 做同层降序，且新增测试覆盖，见 `[src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/path_planner.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/path_planner.py):39`-`80`、`[tests/test_adaptive/test_path_planner.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_adaptive/test_path_planner.py):62`-`78`。  
- F005（topic参数移除）: 通过。工具参数里已无 `topic`，见 `[src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/adaptive.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/ai/tools/adaptive.py):6`-`15`。  

